skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: good deed
des: Good Deed of the Day gives you a good deed to do, so that you can be a better version of you every day. Doing a good thing not only helps bring a smile to you the people around you but also help you feel content. The world needs more good people.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
